[The described bi-national cooperation is highly commendable, exemplary for
other countries in the region. Eight Asian countries have informed the
Office International des Epizooties (OIE) during 2004 of the absence of
HPAI infection from their territories. For their official reports, see
<http://oie.int/downld/AVIAN%20INFLUENZA/A_AI-Asia.htm> - Mod.AS]
